// Script Variable PET_NAME :
"P3148347594" "Ghost Widow"
// Script Variable PET_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4132230600" "Beautiful, mysterious, and deadly. Ghost Widow appears to be an actual spirit from beyond the grave rather than a super with some sort of incorporeal power. Some have said she was once a rising star in the Night Widows when she was slain. Her thirst for vengeance must have been great, for she returned from the void and now serves at Recluse's side. There are rumors that her service isn't entirely voluntary, however. "
// Script Variable PET_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1154458974" "What are you going to do with me now, fools?  You can not kill me!"
// Script Variable PET_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3095170781" "{HeroName}?  This is truly a surprise..."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P2103656255" "Intriguing, {HeroName}. I'm quite interested in hearing why you've helped me."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P1590221852" "<shout>{HeroName}, I will not tolerate these games.<br><br>Get back here at once!"
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P1219820263" "Apprehend Ghost Widow!"
