"P3900920155" "Accompany Ghost Widow to the Pyschic Generator!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2461457485" "Mind Controlled Arachnos Operative"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1038502718" "Could even a mystic as powerful as a Mu Guardian escape this fate? An eternal after-life in service to the Goddess Hequat? Perhaps. But none of them would want anything else than to serve their Goddess as their ancestors once did 14,000 years ago."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3178356647" "Everything must..."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1303933271" "Everyone.  Everyone must be destroyed.<em>Everyone.  Destroyed.  There is no other way."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3772584384" "He dares to control our operatives as well?  Quantum will suffer for this..."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P759143539" "It seems Quantum has far more power at his disposal than we believed.  This doesn't bode well."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P990268398" "I don't understand what Quantum thinks he's doing."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3070685121" "This isn't simple mind control.  They seem to be acting on their own volition!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2070653822" "I must admit... This is a far greater threat than I believed."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P20476466" "This has gone too far.  Where is Quantum!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P202455678" "Recluse as well... These guys are serious."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1410900488" "Reveal your plan and I'll make your death swift, worm."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1939876591" "Interesting.  A hero such as yourself doesn't have the strength to kill their own men. Seems like Quantum has you between a rock and a hard place."

