// IntroString :
"P3813664727" "Paragon City can't afford for criminals to think that the heroes are going to be punished by those in authority. They need to believe that they have <i>absolute</i> authority to put an end to whatever crime is at hand. Anything less than that will risk the city being overrun with those who believe they can find loopholes in the system.<br><br>Releasing Blast Furnace will allow him to continue his work in Paragon!"
// AcceptString :
"P537579377" "Break Blast Furnace out of the Zig"
// SendOffString :
"P2830254619" "You'll have to make your way into the Zig. You're well aware that there are parts of it still under construction from the numerous raids that Arachnos attempts. You can make your way through the courtyard and into the more vulnerable areas in order to get Blast Furnace out!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P191739599" "Break Blast Furnace out of the Zig!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P751983709" "You need to get Blast Furnace back onto the streets as soon as you can!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1393784157" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Above the Law</color></span></scale></font>"

