// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3634509504" "You make your way into the courtyard of the Zig. It looks like the PPD are here in force to ensure nothing happens. You'll have to take down their main Enforcers before you can think about getting Blast Furnace out!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1144478829" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Above the Law</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Blast Furnace is back on the streets in Paragon. You've made the streets that much safer today, even if the PPD don't like it. All that matters is the results, and Blast Furnace is someone who gets them.<br><br>The PPD should remember that the next time they call for someone's help in a situation they can't handle."
